listing_desc.396: Wrong Direction Farm delivers Certified Organic, Pasture Raised Chicken and Turkey, along with our Grass Fed Beef from our family farm directly to customers throughout the Northeast.
listing_desc.444: Our 300 acre farm offers PYO sweet & tart cherries, apples (over 50 varieties!), peaches, nectarines, pears, plums, pumpkins, and a challenging 5-acre corn maze! Our new farm stand offers local fruits and vegetables, local honey, jams, fresh sweet cider, fudge, an on-site bakery,  gifts by local artisans, and more.
